1.3			 *** Version number
***************************
***  medium parameters  ***
***************************
1.060000E+003		*** rho0   = Ambient density rho0 [kg/m^3]
1.578000E+003		*** c0     = Small signal sound velocity [m/s] 
2.000000E-003		*** µ	   = Medium viscosity [Pa*sec]
1.010000E+005		*** P0 	   = Ambient Pressure [Pa]
1.500000E+006		*** fc0    = Frequency at which sound velocity is given [Hz]
4.370000E+000		*** beta   = Nonlinearity parameter
5.200000E-002		*** a_att  = Frequency-dependent attenuation parameter [Np/cm MHz^b]
1.210000E+000		*** b_att  = Power in frequency power attenuation law
*************************************************
***   domain and discretization parameters    ***
*************************************************
3.000010E+001		*** Lx in [mm]
1.501000E+001		*** Ly in [mm]
0.900000E+002		*** Lt in [cycles]
0.000000E+000		*** Sz in [mm]	(Start of the field)
9.010000E+001		*** Lz in [mm]	(length of the field in z)
1.570796E+000		*** Thetax [rad]
1.570796E+000		*** Thetay [rad]
1.570796E+000		*** Thetat [rad]
1.500000E+006		*** freq0  = Fundamental frequency [Hz]
3.500000E+000		*** Fnyq   = Maximum frequency of interest (in fundamental freq)
2					*** Points Per Wavelength
