0	*** Enable (1) the Steepest Descent implementation
0	*** Enable (1) the linearzied Steepest Descent version
0	*** Enable and select the Dual Frequency Modality
0	*** Shift in relation to the DFM (the spatial shift is defined with resptect to the x coordiante and the spatial sampling c0/2*Fnyq*f0)
